{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775846115315,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28752efdeffeMucK6tRnSSb4lm\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78ad45dc001d5UVa0QQ8lWV6N\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78ad37710013I8PbJRl7I0WnO\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28752efdeffeMucK6tRnSSb4lm\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-533f24212d384f30b9a20d384eea4a9b\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-007/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-007/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-007 Design — K8s Reconciler Controller\\n2: \\n3: **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`  \\n4: **Language**: Go  \\n5: **Size**: L  \\n6: **Purpose**: Implement Kubernetes-native reconciler controllers for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs using controller-runtime, providing automated lifecycle management for sandbox resources with proper event handling and status reporting.\\n7: \\n8: ## Overview\\n9: \\n10: This AR implements a proper Kubernetes reconciler pattern using `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` to manage AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter custom resources. The reconcilers will watch for changes to these CRDs and automatically manage the lifecycle of associated sandbox resources, updating status conditions and ensuring the desired state is achieved.\\n11: \\n12: ### Key Requirements\\n13: \\n14: - Watch AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs for create/update/delete events\\n15: - Reconcile sandbox resources using the agent-sandbox API\\n16: - Maintain accurate status conditions (Ready, Error, Progressing, etc.)\\n17: - Handle spec changes gracefully (rolling updates, reconfiguration)\\n18: - Implement proper event recording and finalizer handling\\n19: - Provide metrics for reconciliation performance\\n20: - Support leader election for high availability\\n21: \\n22: ## Architecture\\n23: \\n24: ### Package Structure\\n25: \\n26: ```\\n...\n  Line 29: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775846341671,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28752efdeffeMucK6tRnSSb4lm\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78b0bb74001ssMuxIJH66fcW5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78ad79780014RIpceVvZ4wZ1U\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28752efdeffeMucK6tRnSSb4lm\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-de5297c32dde4cb99db329385e37de5e\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-007 Implementation Plan\\n\\n**Feature:** AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器\\n**Goal:** Implement Kubernetes-native reconciler controllers for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs using controller-runtime to provide automated lifecycle management for sandbox resources with proper event handling and status reporting.\\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\\n- AgentRuntimeReconciler successfully creates and manages sandbox resources\\n- CodeInterpreterReconciler successfully creates and manages sandbox resources\\n- Status conditions are accurately updated during reconciliation (Ready, Error, Progressing, etc.)\\n- Finalizers are properly handled for resource deletion\\n- Events are recorded for all significant operations\\n- Metrics are exposed and can be scraped by Prometheus\\n- Unit tests cover all major code paths\\n- Integration tests validate end-to-end reconciliation\\n- Error handling is robust and provides clear feedback\\n- Reconciler can handle spec changes gracefully\\n- Leader election works correctly in HA deployments\\n**Architecture:** Controller-runtime based reconciler pattern with separate reconcilers for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs, coexisting with existing HTTP-based controller, using agent-sandbox API for sandbox lifecycle management.\\n**Tech Stack:** Go, controller-runtime, client-go, agent-sandbox API, Prometheus metrics, Ginkgo/Gomega testing\\n**前端验证:** No\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Task 1: Create reconciler package directory structure\\n\\n**Files:**\\n- Create: `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler/`\\n\\n**Step 1: Create reconciler directory**\\n\\n```bash\\nmkdir -p pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler\\n```\\n\\n**S...\n  Line 32: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775846359027,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28752efdeffeMucK6tRnSSb4lm\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78b0fdb5001hN5JAQYL42Noyw\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78b0bc50001NimlxyOBqL52vo\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28752efdeffeMucK6tRnSSb4lm\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Created tasks.md with 25 atomic tasks for AR-007 K8s Reconciler controller implementation, following TDD principles with Red-Green-Refactor cycles and frequent commits.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775846359025,\"end\":1775846359025}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z_logs/AR-007_ST-1.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775846257355,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28750a4a5ffeJGGsAj2uxufkDR\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78af7291001jYtAAcwjOP5fTx\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78af5c3c001vgPTHGI7bjAP77\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28750a4a5ffeJGGsAj2uxufkDR\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-46c71680b58a4b7ba05cb979beca2229\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write proposal.md for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器\\n4: Module: pkg/workloadmanager\\n5: Language: Go\\n6: Size: L\\n7: \\n8: Relevant specs:\\n9: --- deployment/client-go.md ---\\n10: # client-go library\\n11: \\n12: Generated Kubernetes client code for API group **`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` / `v1alpha1`**, module path **`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`**. Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Clientset\\n15: \\n16: ### `Interface` (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\\n17: \\n18: ```go\\n19: type Interface interface {\\n20: \\tDiscovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\\n21: \\tRuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\\n22: }\\n23: ```\\n24: \\n25: ### `Clientset` struct\\n26: \\n27: Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and holds `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`.\\n28: \\n29: **Constructors**\\n30: \\n31: - `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\\n32: - `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\\n33: - `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\\n34: - `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\\n35: \\n36: **Group accessor:** `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\\n37: \\n38: ---\\n39: \\n40: ## Typed client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\\n41: \\n42: ### `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`clientset/versioned/...\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775846325035,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28750a4a5ffeJGGsAj2uxufkDR\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78b07b07001zZSjvM7iLEcSy5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78af7300001tuDsX4vXiUqCZh\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28750a4a5ffeJGGsAj2uxufkDR\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-925a21ddc5af4de2ad526ae86f212bc9\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md\",\"content\":\"# AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\\n\\n## 概述\\n\\n| 属性 | 值 |\\n|------|-----|\\n| AR | AR-007 |\\n| Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\\n| Language | Go |\\n| Size | L |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\\n\\n实现一个 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，用于管理 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源：\\n\\n- **AgentRuntime**: 管理 Agent 运行时实例的生命周期\\n- **CodeInterpreter**: 管理代码解释器实例的生命周期\\n\\n控制器将：\\n1. 监听 CRD 资源的创建、更新、删除事件\\n2. 根据 CR spec 协调实际状态向期望状态收敛\\n3. 管理底层 Pod、Service、ConfigMap 等工作负载资源\\n4. 更新 CR status 以反映当前状态\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 2. Scope (范围)\\n\\n### 2.1 In Scope\\n\\n1. **Controller 框架搭建**\\n   - 使用 `controller-runtime` 框架 (sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime)\\n   - 集成 client-go 生成的客户端代码\\n   - 实现 Reconcile 循环\\n\\n2. **AgentRuntime 控制器**\\n   - 监听 AgentRuntime CR 的变更\\n   - 创建/更新/删除关联的 Kubernetes 资源 (Pod, Service, ConfigMap, Secret)\\n   - 状态同步：Phase, Conditions, PodStatus, Endpoint 等\\n   - 支持多副本部署策略\\n\\n3. **CodeInterpreter 控制器**\\n   - 监听 CodeInterpreter CR 的变更\\n   - 管理解释器容器的生命周期\\n   - 状态同步：Phase, Conditions, ResourceUsage 等\\n\\n4. **通用功能**\\n   - Event 记录 (Normal/Warning)\\n   - Finalizer 处理 (资源清理)\\n   - OwnerReference 设置 (级联删除)\\n   - 领导选举 (Leader Election) 支持多实例部署\\n\\n### 2.2 Out of Scope\\n\\n- Webhook (Validating/Mutating) - 由独立 AR 处理\\n- CRD 定义本身 - 假设已存在\\n- 具体业务逻辑 (Agent 执行、解释器逻辑) - 由其他模块处理\\n- 监控指标暴露 - 由独立 AR 处理\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\\n\\n### 3.1 新增文件\\n\\n```\\npkg/workloadmanager/\\n├── controller.go              # 控制器入口，注册 Manager\\n├── agentruntime_controller.go # AgentRuntime Reconciler 实现\\n├── codeinterpreter_controller.go # CodeInterp...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z_logs/AR-007_ST-0.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775846192952,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28751a2d8ffecSNMhM59C6FXsB\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78ae746f001FJUYXMiuYZyFG3\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78ae5e250012cQGtwPEijkNw6\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28751a2d8ffecSNMhM59C6FXsB\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll explore the repository structure to understand the change scaffold format and create the AR-007 directory.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775846192950,\"end\":1775846192950}}}\n  Line 18: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775846217344,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28751a2d8ffecSNMhM59C6FXsB\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78aecf2d001XGrWFVNS5Rp5CO\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78aeb63b001w5PvaLIALf6TaI\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28751a2d8ffecSNMhM59C6FXsB\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I understand the scaffold structure. Let me create the AR-007 dire