me CRD (informers)\\n25:   │   ├─ Watches: Sandbox Pods (owned by AgentRuntime)\\n26:   │   └─ Reconciles: Spec → Pod creation/update, Status sync\\n27:   └─ CodeInterpreter Reconciler\\n28:       ├─ Watches: CodeInterpreter CRD (informers)\\n29:       ├─ Watches: Sandbox Pods (owned by CodeInterpreter)\\n30:       └─ Reconciles: Spec → Pod creation/update, Status sync\\n31:   ↓\\n32: Kubernetes Client Layer\\n33:   ├─ typed client (AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInt...\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775845798130,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2875971e6ffeIxBNdiOINqBuQE\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78a6d8b5001MdAw5nzs8p2LvM\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78a6c6f60010vzhTyYyjV1Pc5\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2875971e6ffeIxBNdiOINqBuQE\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_2f95625be92a41f8bd334743\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 Tasks\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n| Item | Value |\\n|------|-------|\\n| AR | AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 |\\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\\n| Language | Go |\\n| Size | L |\\n| Stage | ST-3 completed |\\n\\n## Atomic Tasks\\n\\n### Phase 1: Data Structures & Types\\n\\n- [ ] **TASK-001**: Define `Reconciler` interface in `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager.go`\\n  - Methods: `Run(ctx context.Context)`, `Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req Request) (Result, error)`\\n  - Document each method purpose\\n\\n- [ ] **TASK-002**: Define `Request` struct in `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager.go`\\n  - Fields: `Namespace` (string), `Name` (string)\\n  - Document usage in reconciliation loop\\n\\n- [ ] **TASK-003**: Define `Result` struct in `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager.go`\\n  - Fields: `Requeue` (bool), `RequeueAfter` (time.Duration)\\n  - Document requeue behavior and priorities\\n\\n- [ ] **TASK-004**: Define `ReconcilerConfig` struct in `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager.go`\\n  - Fields: `ResyncPeriod`, `MaxRetries`, `RateLimitQPS`, `RateLimitBurst`, `ConcurrentReconciles`, `EnableLeaderElection`, `LeaderElectionNamespace`, `LeaderElectionName`\\n  - All fields documented with comments\\n\\n- [ ] **TASK-005**: Implement `DefaultReconcilerConfig()` function\\n  - Returns default configuration per design spec\\n  - Defaults: ResyncPeriod=10m, MaxRetries=5, RateLimitQPS=10, RateLimitBurst=20, ConcurrentReconciles=2\\n\\n- [ ] **TASK-006**: Define error constants in `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/errors.go`\\n  - Constants: `ErrReconcileFailed`, `ErrPodCreationFailed`, `ErrPodUpdateFailed`, `ErrStatusUpdateFailed`...\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775845807501,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2875971e6ffeIxBNdiOINqBuQE\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78a88a27001xGh7QuSc2DBjrn\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78a87134001Hk4EwGlUmkEfw1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2875971e6ffeIxBNdiOINqBuQE\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Created `/changes/AR-007/tasks.md` with 12 phases and 90+ atomic tasks covering:\\n\\n- **Phase 1-3**: Core types, ControllerManager, AgentRuntimeReconciler\\n- **Phase 4-7**: CodeInterpreterReconciler, SandboxProcessor, StatusUpdater, OwnerReference\\n- **Phase 8-9**: Metrics and error handling/retry logic\\n- **Phase 10-12**: Configuration, comprehensive TDD testing, documentation\\n\\nTasks follow the same atomic, independently verifiable pattern as AR-005 and AR-006 with clear acceptance criteria and dependencies.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775845807499,\"end\":1775845807499}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-007_ST-1.log:\n  Line 5: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775845682535,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287595d91ffeYSxWJsWkpfhK3g\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78a6ad30001RdN7SreuEP5rw2\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78a6a3520017sq0zJ7qe92Hzg\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287595d91ffeYSxWJsWkpfhK3g\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-05c46f5b11a5448a888d6a4b990d6aff\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmar