\n1. **Controller initialization**\\n   - GIVEN a valid `rest.Config`\\n   - WHEN `NewWorkloadManager(config)` is called\\n   - THEN a `WorkloadManager` instance is returned with initialized clientset, informers, and work queue\\n\\n2. **Informer registration**\\n   - GIVEN a WorkloadManager instance\\n   - WHEN informers are started via `Start(stopCh)`\\n   - THEN AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter informers register event handlers (Add/Update/Delete)\\n\\n3. **Lister wiring**\\n   - GIVEN running informers\\n   - WHEN a reconciliation cycle begins\\n   - THEN listers provide cached read access without API server calls\\n\\n---\\n\\n### REQ-002: AgentRuntime Reconciliation\\n\\n**GIVEN** an AgentRuntime CR is created/...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-007_ST-1.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775845254152,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2875fec33ffefhYBum3nJkteaU\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78a01f5e001sECdt7Dig127UP\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78a014ba001t2Ke6LwJeqGM5h\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2875fec33ffefhYBum3nJkteaU\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_0f0254810b414353a138e15c\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write proposal.md for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器\\n4: Module: pkg/workloadmanager\\n5: Language: Go\\n6: Size: L\\n7: \\n8: Relevant specs:\\n9: --- deployment/client-go.md ---\\n10: # client-go library\\n11: \\n12: Generated Kubernetes client code for API group **`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` / `v1alpha1`**, module path **`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`**. Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube