cumentation provided and the existing codebase structure, I'll write a comprehensive proposal.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775845291410,\"end\":1775845291410}}}\n  Line 32: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775845371803,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2875fec33ffefhYBum3nJkteaU\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d78a0b595001CUJYQ8rxbwZY4E\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d78a0a663001KO1eDwExwaDQ4H\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2875fec33ffefhYBum3nJkteaU\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_468684d16c3b45bba364b28f\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/proposal.md\",\"content\":\"# AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\nThis proposal defines the design and implementation of a Kubernetes-native Reconciler controller for the AgentCube project. The Reconciler controller watches `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` CRDs and ensures the actual cluster state matches the desired state specified in the CR specs. The goal is to:\\n\\n1. **Implement the Kubernetes Operator Pattern** — Use controller-runtime to build event-driven reconcilers that react to CRD changes\\n2. **Automate sandbox lifecycle management** — Create, update, and delete sandbox pods based on CRD spec changes\\n3. **Maintain CRD status consistency** — Continuously reconcile CRD status with actual sandbox pod state\\n4. **Provide extensible reconciliation hooks** — Allow future extensions for custom lifecycle logic\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager` (reconciler package)  \\n**Language:** Go  \\n**Size:** L\\n\\nThis AR covers:\\n\\n- **In scope:**\\n  - Reconciler implementation for `AgentRuntime` CRD\\n  - Reconciler implementation for `CodeInterpreter` CRD\\n  - Integration with existing client-go types, listers, and informers\\n  - Sandbox pod creation and lifecycle management\\n  - CRD status update logic\\n  - Unit tests and integration tests for reconcilers\\n  - Controller manager setup and initialization\\n\\n- **Out of scope:**\\n  - HTTP API changes to WorkloadManager (AR-004)\\n  - Router or session routing logic\\n  - Redis persistence layer changes\\n  - Volcano scheduler integration (future A...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-017_ST-6.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775845229050,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28762fd77ffe2wOKfgwZXpcMby\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d789d10f5001kKBa3o0xu8Zser\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d789d03870015A3kHRZgQXw1Nu\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28762fd77ffe2wOKfgwZXpcMby\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"task\",\"callID\":\"call_7c9f79165e4e41e1b39403ad\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"description\":\"Explore agentcube project structure\",\"prompt\":\"Explore the project at /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z thoroughly. I need to understand:\\n\\n1. The overall project structure (list top-level directories and key subdirectories)\\n2. Find any files related to:\\n   - `pkg/picod` directory\\n   - JWT middleware\\n   - client-go code generation\\n   - Kubernetes client code (runtime/v1alpha1, AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter)\\n   - Any spec documents or AR (acceptance requirement) files\\n3. Check for test files\\n4. Look for any `deployment/client-go.md` or similar spec files\\n\\nReturn a comprehensive summary of the project structure and all relevant file paths found.\",\"subagent_type\":\"explore\"},\"output\":\"task_id: ses_28762deeaffeCpf2hZv7X906Bt (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\\n\\n<task_result>\\nHere is a comprehensive summary of the project:\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Project Overview: AgentCube\\n\\n**AgentCube** is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents. It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\\n\\n**Go Module:** `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\\n**Go Version:** 1.25.0\\n**Kubernetes API Group:** `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. Top-Level Directory Structure\\n\\n```\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/\\n|-- .sdd_prompt.md            # SDD (Spec-Driven Development) prompt file\\n|-- changes/                   # AR (Acceptance Requirement) change directories (A...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-007_ST-0.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775845220141,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287606ff0ffeG0bHerHlvQVmkJ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d789f9cfe001WuXn1O7tFfEDQo\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d789f9102001Qp54ZsROi9A7HQ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287606ff0ffeG0bHerHlvQVmkJ\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll create the change directory scaffold for AR-007. Let me first check the existing changes directory structure to follow the project conventions.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775845220139,\"end\":1775845220139}}}\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775845241716,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287606ff0ffeG0bHerHlvQVmkJ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d789fe6ea001nkjjgpId10odQr\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d789fc83c001pgJq8pR3nbXPKE\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287606ff0ffeG0bHerHlvQVmkJ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_712ae4353f87477484f24ba5\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-007/status.json\",\"content\":\"{\\n  \\\"ar\\\": \\\"AR-007\\\",\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"K8s Reconciler 控制器\\\",\\n  \\\"module\\\": \\\"pkg/workloadmanager\\\",\\n  \\\"language\\\": \\\"Go\\\",\\n  \\\"size\\\": \\\"L\\\",\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"initialized\\\",\\n  \\\"created\\\": \\\"2026-04-11\\\",\\n  \\\"completed\\\": null\\n}\\n\"},\"output\":\"Wrote file successfully