{"type":"text","timestamp":1775846595223,"sessionID":"ses_2874c420effey6lfKnjjU44hbI","part":{"id":"prt_d78b476ad001uFnLRR4YuyrIj4","messageID":"msg_d78b46ab30011IaONsb5QuPmqC","sessionID":"ses_2874c420effey6lfKnjjU44hbI","type":"text","text":"Based on my review of the AR-007 change documentation and implementation files, here's the archive summary:\n\n---\n\n## AR-007 — K8s Reconciler 控制器 Archive Summary\n\n### Completed (Phase 1-9, ST-3)\n\n**Core Infrastructure:**\n- ✅ `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager.go` - ControllerManager with informer lifecycle management\n- ✅ `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/interface.go` - Reconciler interface, Request/Result types, ReconcilerConfig\n- ✅ `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/errors.go` - Error types and retryable error detection\n- ✅ `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/metrics.go` - Prometheus metrics for reconciliation\n\n**Reconciler Implementation:**\n- ✅ `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler.go` - AgentRuntimeReconciler with full reconciliation loop\n- ✅ `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sandbox_processor.go` - Sandbox pod building and update logic\n- ✅ `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_updater.go` - CRD status update from pod state\n- ✅ `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/owner_reference.go` - Owner reference management for garbage collection\n\n**Design Documentation:**\n- ✅ Comprehensive `design.md` (1387 lines) with architecture, data structures, API contracts, error handling, testing strategy, and client-go integration patterns\n\n---\n\n### Deferred (Phase 10-12, ST-4+)\n\n**Not Implemented:**\n- ❌ **CodeInterpreterReconciler** - Separate reconciler for CodeInterpreter CRD (design mentions it but only AgentRuntime reconciler implemented)\n- ❌ **Configuration flags** - Command-line flags and environment variable integration in `cmd/workload-manager/main.go`\n- ❌ **Main integration** - Reconciler startup integration with WorkloadManager HTTP server\n- ❌ **Tests** - All unit tests, integration tests with envtest, and coverage verification (no `*_test.go` files in reconciler directory)\n- ❌ **Graceful shutdown** - Workqueue draining and shutdown sequence\n- ❌ **Documentation** - Godoc comments, package documentation, README updates\n\n**Status:** Design-complete (ST-3), implementation ~60% complete. Core reconciler framework and AgentRuntime reconciliation functional, but missing tests, CodeInterpreter reconciler, and production integration.","time":{"start":1775846595221,"end":1775846595221}}}
